OL,3,CFootpath unveiled in honour of
OL,4,Cstalking victim
OL,6,FA footpath has been officially opened
OL,7,Fin honour of a young woman who was
OL,8,Fkilled by her stalker.
OL,10,FGracie Spinks was 23 when she was
OL,11,Fstabbed to death by former co-worker
OL,12,FMichael Sellers in Duckmanton, near
OL,13,FChesterfield, in 2021.
OL,15,FOn Friday her father, Richard, helped
OL,16,Fto open the new Gracie Spinks Way
OL,17,Fclose to where she was attacked as she
OL,18,Ftended her horse.
