OL,3,CFootpath unveiled in honour of
OL,4,Cstalking victim
OL,6,FStaveley Town Council, which funded
OL,7,Fthe signs, hopes it will become a
OL,8,Flandmark and help to promote community
OL,9,Fsafety.
OL,11,FMr Spinks said: "To have it there in
OL,12,Ftribute to Gracie's life and what she
OL,13,Fwanted to achieve, on a trail that she
OL,14,Fused with her horse so often, is a
OL,15,Fgreat thing."
OL,17,FGracie was attacked four months after
OL,18,Fshe first reported Sellers to
OL,19,FDerbyshire Police after he became
OL,20,Fobsessed with her.
