OL,4,Cstalking victim
OL,6,FOfficers had warned him to stay away
OL,7,Ffrom her, but failed to act when a bag
OL,8,Fof weapons was found close to the
OL,9,Fstables where Gracie kept her horse
OL,10,FPaddy.
OL,12,FShe was found in the field near
OL,13,FStaveley Road in Duckmanton and died
OL,14,Fat the scene.
OL,16,FSellers' body was found a short
OL,17,Fdistance away after he killed himself.
