OL,6,FThe law would also ensure officers
OL,7,Fhave enough training to deal with
OL,8,Fstalking and for a stalking advocate
OL,9,Fto be available to act as a liaison
OL,10,Fbetween the police and victims.
OL,12,FMr Spinks said: "We have a lot of work
OL,13,Fbut we have made a lot of progress
OL,14,Falready and maybe saved some lives
OL,15,Fwith our campaign."
OL,17,FHe added: "Police still need to make
OL,18,Fchanges with regard to taking on
OL,19,Fadvocates and stalking coordinators."
